{"id":274,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":274,"title":"Revelation 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","John sees fire and desolation poured out during the seventh seal and preceding the Second Coming."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.1","order":"03.29.008.27654"},["b","1"],"And when he had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"opened"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"seventh seal"],", there was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"silence"],"in heaven about the space of half an hour."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.2","order":"03.29.008.27655"},["b","2"],"And I saw the seven angels which stood before God; and to them were given seven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"trumpets"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.3","order":"03.29.008.27656"},["b","3"],"And another angel came and stood at the altar, having a golden censer; and there was given unto him much",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"incense"],", that he should offer",["i","it"],"with the prayers of all saints upon the golden altar which was before the throne."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.4","order":"03.29.008.27657"},["b","4"],"And the smoke of the incense,",["i","which came"],"with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"prayers"],"of the saints, ascended up before God out of the angel’s hand."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.5","order":"03.29.008.27658"},["b","5"],"And the angel took the censer, and filled it with fire of the altar, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cast"],["i","it"],"into the earth: and there were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"voices"],", and thunderings, and lightnings, and an earthquake."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.6","order":"03.29.008.27659"},["b","6"],"And the seven angels which had the seven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"trumpets"],"prepared themselves to sound."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.7","order":"03.29.008.27660"},["b","7"],"The first angel sounded, and there followed hail and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"fire"],"mingled with blood, and they were cast upon the earth: and the third part of trees was burnt up, and all green grass was burnt up."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.8","order":"03.29.008.27661"},["b","8"],"And the second angel sounded, and as it were a great mountain burning with fire was cast into the sea: and the third part of the sea became",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"blood"],";"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.9","order":"03.29.008.27662"},["b","9"],"And the third part of the creatures which were in the sea, and had life, died; and the third part of the ships were destroyed."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.10","order":"03.29.008.27663"},["b","10"],"And the third angel sounded, and there",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fell"],"a great star from heaven, burning as it were a lamp, and it fell upon the third part of the rivers, and upon the fountains of waters;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.11","order":"03.29.008.27664"},["b","11"],"And the name of the star is called Wormwood: and the third part of the waters became wormwood; and many men died of the waters, because they were made bitter."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.12","order":"03.29.008.27665"},["b","12"],"And the fourth angel sounded, and the third part of the sun was smitten, and the third part of the moon, and the third part of the stars; so as the third part of them was darkened, and the day shone not for a third part of it, and the night likewise."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.13","order":"03.29.008.27666"},["b","13"],"And I beheld, and heard an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"angel"],"flying through the midst of heaven, saying with a loud voice,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"Woe"],", woe, woe, to the inhabiters of the earth by reason of the other voices of the trumpet of the three angels, which are yet to sound!"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.1a","order":"03.29.008.27667"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.13"},"D&C 77:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.1b","order":"03.29.008.27669"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.1c","order":"03.29.008.27671"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/silence"},"TG Silence"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.2a","order":"03.29.008.27673"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.12"},"D&C 77:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.3a","order":"03.29.008.27675"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/16.13.12-13"},"Lev. 16:13 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/16.40.36-40"},"Num. 16:40 (36–40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.4a","order":"03.29.008.27677"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.8"},"Rev. 5:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.5a","order":"03.29.008.27679"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.2"},"Ezek. 10:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.5b","order":"03.29.008.27681"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.90"},"D&C 88:90"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.6a","order":"03.29.008.27683"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.12"},"D&C 77:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.7a","order":"03.29.008.27685"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/9.24.22-25"},"Ex. 9:24 (22–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.8a","order":"03.29.008.27687"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-symbolism-of"},"TG Blood, Symbolism of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.10a","order":"03.29.008.27689"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.12"},"Isa. 14:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.13a","order":"03.29.008.27691"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.92"},"D&C 88:92"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.13b","order":"03.29.008.27693"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/7.22"},"Hel. 7:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.5"},"D&C 5:5"],"."]]}
